    "longBusinessSummary": "Saigon Telecommunication & Technologies Corporation provides telecommunications infrastructure services in Vietnam. The company engages in the trading of electric-electronic equipment, materials, machinery and equipment, and telephone cards, and internet cards; transmission, terminator, and protection equipment for IT; and computers and software, as well as installation, repair, and maintenance of computers. It also provides technological constancy services; and value added, data and information access, data handling, and electronic data exchanging services, as well as acts as internet and telecom postal service agent; manufactures electronic components; and designs and installs network infrastructures. In addition, the company is involved in trading of real estates; right to use land being owned, used or leased; infrastructures in industrial parks; industrial park, urban residential area, and informatics technological zone; builds industrial, civil, traffic works, road and bridge, irrigational, and electrical works; invests in infrastructures of industrial parks; builds industrial park, urban residential area, and informatics technological zone, as well as houses, railways, roads, electricity works, water supply and drainage; and functioning as brokerage agent. Further, it exploits, treats and provides with water; produces, transmits, and distributes power; setting up consolidated electronic information page; repairs electrical equipment; installs electricity system; advertising; and markets research and public opinion poll, as well as organizes trade introduction and promotion; events, fairs, exhibitions, conferences, seminars, and festivals. Saigon Telecommunication & Technologies Corporation was incorporated in 2002 and is headquartered in Ho Chi Minh City, Vietnam.",
